Hi @Bastiane
When you are referring to partial results are you referring to partial rows from the formed table in each doc.
As Eric mentioned, there are two option need to have selected:
1. Enable multi-page tables and checkboxes (enable this before any documents are uploaded).
2. Use a prompt like "Extract all tables" in prompt phrase and for complex phrases like this we need to enable "Complex prompt"
The second table at times is picked up - but with 1 item there it does not look like a table, so likely model does not pick it up always.
For first clear table - I do see all the rows in all docs from above you shared.
Btw, I have been testing this on aihub-uat.internal env
cc: @Lalit
